		<div class="post" id="post-4687077">
		<div class="long">
			<div class="head">
									<div class="options">
						<a href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,4687077)" class="btn btn-default btn-small btn-sm">Fold</a>
					</div>
								<div class="title" id="post-title-4687077">
																		Author Post
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppermint-legos" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5515758); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5515758&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610163659" alt="peppermint_legos" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5515758)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppermint-legos" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5515758); return false;" >peppermint_legos</a></span> <span class="odate time_1592069094 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">13 Jun 2020 17:24</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4687077">
									

<p>A love letter to stage fright, unsung containment specialists, and this wonderful imaginative community.</p>
<p>Huge thank-you to critters <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dianaberry" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3444428); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3444428&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592069094" alt="DianaBerry" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3444428)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dianaberry" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3444428); return false;">DianaBerry</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/truc-linh" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5813515); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5813515&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592069094" alt="Truc Linh" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5813515)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/truc-linh" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5813515); return false;">Truc Linh</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sonderance" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6091992); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6091992&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592069094" alt="Sonderance" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6091992)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sonderance" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6091992); return false;">Sonderance</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(776854); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=776854&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592069094" alt="Tanhony" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=776854)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(776854); return false;">Tanhony</a></span> for their input, edits, and greenlights.</p>
<p>Credit to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djoric" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(388108); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=388108&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592069094" alt="Djoric" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=388108)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djoric" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(388108); return false;">Djoric</a></span> for creating THE DEER.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+Fun&nbsp;Facts</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-Fun&nbsp;Facts</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<ul>
<li>Part of a series/canon I'd love to write about the Foundation's HR Department. Natalie Burman <strong>will return</strong>.</li>
<li>I know this might slightly contradict 2845's broken masquerade, and the clause of staff being stuck on-site. There's more lore about that in my mind, and it might show up in another piece someday&#8230;but no promises, and feel free to fill in the gaps yourself.</li>
<li>Grandpa Eldon, his bari sax, and his draft dodge are real, though Vietnam replaced Korea. He will strike up a conversation with literally anyone.</li>
<li>Inspiration for this came from my own experience in the staffing/recruiting industry, which feels like an unexplored narrative in the Foundation with some (literal) killer potential. I haven't found any tales/SCPs that directly involve HR, but if anyone has any suggestions I'd love to read them!</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>Thank you for reading!</p>

							</div>

								
					
