			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4687142">
									

<blockquote>
<p>It was a hundred million people: an infinite audience packed into a single, impossible face. I saw — or imagined — antlers and ice and shimmering metal spheres and, behind that, something more. A warped song, a counter-melody, some sort of response that this thing was preparing, just for me.</p>
<div style="clear:both; height: 0px; font-size: 1px"></div>
<p>It tilted its head, and the entire world bent to match.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Awesome prose, loved how you delve into the eldritch/not quite right nature of the Deer and its conprocs. Heavy +1.</p>

